high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato inside on the bottom shelf then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take the tomato out then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave then turn right to face the sink.
Put the chilled tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the sink.

high_descs: turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the right and go to the counter
pick up the tomato from the counter top
turn to the right twice and go to the front of the refrigerator and turn to the left and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and put the tomato on the bottom right shelf and close the door and wait and open the door and pick up the tomato and close the refrigerator door
turn to the left and go to the counter and turn to the right facing the sink
put the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a cold tomato in the sink

high_descs: Turn to your left, then turn right to go to the counter adjacent to the stove.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and chill it, then take it out.
Turn left and go forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the sink.
